title: Eric Johnson - Ah Via Musicom [EAC+FLAC]
description:
"Ah Via Musicom" is guitar virtuoso Eric Johnson's most famous album. It contains the well-known masterpiece "Cliffs of Dover", recently grown more famous after being featured on the best-seller videogame "Guitar Hero III: Legends of Rock". 

Encoded from the original CD with EAC and FLAC, 100% accuracy. Check out Eric Johnson's wikipedia page: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eric_Johnson


Please buy the original CD if you like this. You find it cheap and it's not shit we're talking about: it's really, REALLY good music. Please support these great artists.
